intro: Here goes your questions, Maya, asked with Easy difficulty for the Data Scientist  role (2 questions).
questions: 1.  Describe a time you had to explain complex data findings to a non-technical audience. What techniques did you use to ensure they understood the key takeaways?

2.  This job requires collaborating with engineers and product designers.  Give me an example of a time you successfully collaborated with a team whose skillset was significantly different from your own to achieve a shared objective.
